    <mxCell id="18" value="Go AIS Receiver
(EKS / Kubernetes)
2–20 pods per topic  (HPA)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fde68a;strokeColor=#d97706;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="140" y="206" width="260" height="68" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="19" value="• Multi-part NMEA fragment assembly (source attribution)
• Source tagging: copies s: header to all fragment parts
• Exactly-once publish via Kafka transactions
• IAM-authenticated MSK producer (SASL/SSL port 9098)
• HPA autoscales on CloudWatch consumer-group lag metric" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=8;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="430" y="202" width="548" height="78" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="20" value="Amazon MSK — Source Topics  (3 brokers · 3 AZs · replication factor = 3)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef9c3;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="30" y="294" width="970" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="21" value="ais-terrestrial
32 partitions" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef08a;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="80" y="322" width="155" height="58" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="22" value="ais-satellite
32 partitions" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef08a;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="250" y="322" width="155" height="58" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="23" value="ais-roaming
32 partitions" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef08a;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="420" y="322" width="155" height="58" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="24" value="• SASL/SSL + AWS IAM auth (port 9098)
• 7-day retention → full replay on consumer reset
• Replication = 3 → survives single broker or AZ failure
• Scalability: add partitions + brokers with zero downtime
• Durability: committed offsets survive full MSK restart" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=8;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="600" y="318" width="378" height="78" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="25" value="Flink Job 1 — Parser / Validator  (Bronze Layer)   |  Parallelism: 4   |  Checkpoint: EXACTLY_ONCE every 60 s   |  Restart: 3× / 10 s delay" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dcfce7;strokeColor=#16a34a;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="30" y="410" width="970" height="220" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
