    <mxCell id="37" value="Side output → DLQ (unparseable lines)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fecaca;strokeColor=#dc2626;fontSize=8;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="355" y="520" width="230" height="20" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="38" value="5-min state TTL (Type24 join window)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#bbf7d0;strokeColor=#16a34a;fontSize=8;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="655" y="520" width="230" height="20" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="39" value="Exactly-Once Checkpointing  |  State backend: RocksDB (incremental snapshots)  |  Back-pressure: Flink credit-based flow control" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#bbf7d0;strokeColor=#16a34a;fontSize=8;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="550" width="920" height="22" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="40" value="Fault tolerance: restore from last checkpoint (&lt; 60 s RPO)  |  Flink restart = 3 fixed-delay attempts  |  MSK offsets committed at checkpoint" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef9c3;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=8;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="578" width="920" height="22" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="41" value="Scalability: parallelism ≤ MSK partition count (32)  |  Add TaskManagers → Flink rebalances automatically  |  Max ~50 K msgs/sec at p=32" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dbeafe;strokeColor=#3b82f6;fontSize=8;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="606" width="920" height="22" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="42" value="Job 1 Outputs" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f3e8ff;strokeColor=#9333ea;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="30" y="638" width="970" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="43" value="S3 Bronze — Parquet
s3://…/ais-bronze-ingest/
year=Y/month=M/day=D/
Snappy compressed" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e9d5ff;strokeColor=#9333ea;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="70" y="666" width="200" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="44" value="MSK  ais.ingest
(JSON per record)
32 partitions" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef08a;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="300" y="666" width="165" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="45" value="MSK  ais.parse.dlq
(DLQ — side output)
unparseable NMEA" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fecaca;strokeColor=#dc2626;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="500" y="666" width="170" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="46" value="• Parquet: columnar, 10:1 compression vs JSON
• Hive partitions → date-pruning in Athena queries
• S3: 11-nines durability, lifecycle → Glacier 90 d
• ais.ingest consumed by Job 2 downstream
• DLQ: 7-day retention, operator can replay &amp; fix" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=8;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="695" y="662" width="302" height="78" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="47" value="Flink Job 2 — MSK Router  (Silver Layer)   |  Parallelism: 4   |  Checkpoint: EXACTLY_ONCE every 60 s" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dcfce7;strokeColor=#16a34a;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="30" y="754" width="970" height="138" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="48" value="Route by msgType
1 / 2 / 3  →  ais.type1  (Position Reports)
5          →  ais.type5  (Voyage &amp; Static)
18 / 19    →  ais.type18 (Class B Position)
24         →  ais.type24 (Class B Static)
27         →  ais.type27 (Long Range AIS)
unknown    →  ais.router.dlq" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#86efac;strokeColor=#16a34a;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="80" y="782" width="360" height="98" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="49" value="• Fan-out: 1 input record → 1 typed output topic
• Exactly-once with MSK transactional producer
• Type-sharding → each consumer sees only relevant msgs
• Fault: job restarts from checkpoint; MSK txn aborted
• Scalability: each typed topic independently partitioned
• DLQ: unknown/malformed msgType records preserved" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=8;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="470" y="778" width="500" height="98" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="50" value="Amazon MSK — Typed Topics  (Silver · replication = 3)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef9c3;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="30" y="900" width="970" height="95" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="51" value="ais.type1
Position" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef08a;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="55" y="928" width="122" height="52" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="52" value="ais.type5
Voyage" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef08a;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="190" y="928" width="122" height="52" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="53" value="ais.type18
Class B" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef08a;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="325" y="928" width="122" height="52" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="54" value="ais.type24
Static" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef08a;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="460" y="928" width="122" height="52" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="55" value="ais.type27
Long Rng" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef08a;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="595" y="928" width="122" height="52" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="56" value="ais.router
.dlq" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fecaca;strokeColor=#dc2626;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="730" y="928" width="108" height="52" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="57" value="Flink Job 3 — Quality Filter  (Gold Layer)   |  Parallelism: 4   |  Checkpoint: EXACTLY_ONCE every 60 s" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dcfce7;strokeColor=#16a34a;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="30" y="1003" width="970" height="148" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="58" value="1. Dedup: MMSI + timestamp (30 s keyed window)
2. Coord validation: lat ∈ [−90, 90]  lon ∈ [−180, 180]
3. Quality score: field completeness (0.0 – 1.0)
4. Threshold filter: score ≥ 0.7 (configurable)
5. Iceberg upsert: keyed by MMSI + event time" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#86efac;strokeColor=#16a34a;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="80" y="1030" width="380" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="59" value="• Iceberg: ACID transactions, time travel, schema evolution
• Upsert semantics: late-arriving data corrects prior records
• Exactly-once via Iceberg commit protocol (2-phase commit)
• Dedup prevents double-counting from replay / retries
• Fault: Iceberg rolls back incomplete txn on restart
• Scalability: Iceberg table sharding by MMSI hash range" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=8;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="490" y="1026" width="490" height="110" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="60" value="Gold Layer — Analytics-Ready" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f3e8ff;strokeColor=#9333ea;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="30" y="1159" width="970" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="61" value="S3 Iceberg Gold
s3://…/ais-gold/
MMSI partitioned
time-travel enabled" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e9d5ff;strokeColor=#9333ea;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="60" y="1187" width="195" height="68" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="62" value="AWS Glue
Data Catalog
(Iceberg schema
&amp; table registry)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e9d5ff;strokeColor=#9333ea;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="278" y="1187" width="165" height="68" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="63" value="Amazon Athena
(serverless SQL
partition pruning
Pay-per-scan)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#bfdbfe;strokeColor=#3b82f6;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="466" y="1187" width="165" height="68" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="64" value="Amazon
QuickSight
(Fleet dashboards
real-time)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#bfdbfe;strokeColor=#3b82f6;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="654" y="1187" width="165" height="68" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="65" value="• Time travel: SELECT … AS OF TIMESTAMP
• Schema evolution: add fields without full rewrite
• Lifecycle: 1 yr hot S3 → Glacier → expire
• Athena: predicate pushdown on Iceberg metadata" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=8;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="840" y="1183" width="148" height="78" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="66" value="Fault Tolerance &amp; Durability" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fefce8;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1060" y="62" width="610" height="348" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="67" value="S3 Checkpoints  (all 3 Flink jobs)
s3://bucket/flink-checkpoints/{job1, job2, job3}/
Retained on cancellation  |  Incremental (RocksDB delta)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef9c3;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1078" y="100" width="574" height="58" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="68" value="Checkpoint config (per job)
• Interval: 60 s   |   Min pause between: 30 s
• Max concurrent: 1   |   Mode: EXACTLY_ONCE (barriers)
• Storage: S3 via Flink S3 filesystem plugin
• Incremental RocksDB → only delta written each cycle" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef9c3;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1078" y="170" width="574" height="80" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="69" value="MSK Durability
• Replication factor 3 across 3 AZs
• Retention 7 days → replay from any offset
• Survives single broker failure (no data loss)
• Consumer group offset committed at checkpoint" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef9c3;strokeColor=#ca8a04;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1078" y="262" width="574" height="78" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="70" value="S3 durability: 99.999999999 % (11 nines)
RPO &lt; 60 s  |  RTO ~ 2 min (restart + warmup)
Flink restore: replay MSK from last checkpoint offset" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=8;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1078" y="352" width="574" height="48" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="71" value="Retry &amp; Error Handling" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff1f2;strokeColor=#e11d48;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1060" y="418" width="610" height="290" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="72" value="Flink Restart Strategy
Type: Fixed Delay   |   Attempts: 3   |   Delay: 10 s
Trigger: task failure, OOM, uncaught exception
After 3 failures → job FAILED → CloudWatch alarm" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fecdd3;strokeColor=#e11d48;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1078" y="452" width="574" height="72" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="73" value="Error Routing (DLQ strategy per job)
• Job 1: unparseable NMEA → ais.parse.dlq (side output)
• Job 2: unknown msgType → ais.router.dlq
• Job 3: invalid coords / low quality → logged + skipped
• DLQ retention: 7 days  |  replayable after operator fix" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fecdd3;strokeColor=#e11d48;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1078" y="536" width="574" height="95" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="74" value="Back-pressure: Flink credit-based flow control
Slow consumers automatically slow MSK readers
No data loss — source re-reads from committed offset
CloudWatch alarm: DLQ rate &gt; 1 % of ingest rate" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=8;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1078" y="642" width="574" height="56" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="75" value="Scalability" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f0fdf4;strokeColor=#16a34a;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1060" y="716" width="610" height="242" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="76" value="Horizontal scaling levers
• MSK: add partitions / brokers live (zero downtime)
• Flink: add TaskManager pods → auto rebalance operators
• Go Receiver: KEDA HPA on consumer-group lag metric
• Max Flink parallelism = MSK partition count (32)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#bbf7d0;strokeColor=#16a34a;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1078" y="752" width="574" height="88" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="77" value="Throughput estimates (p=32, 4 TMs)
• Ingest: ~50 K msgs/sec  (source topics)
• After Job 1 parsing: ~42 K/sec (DLQ ~2 %)
• Gold Iceberg writes: ~35 K/sec (after dedup)
Scale-out: double partitions → double throughput" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=8;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1078" y="852" width="574" height="96" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="78" value="Security" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#eff6ff;strokeColor=#3b82f6;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1060" y="966" width="610" height="198" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="79" value="Identity &amp; Access
• MSK: SASL/SSL + AWS IAM (port 9098, TLS 1.2+)
• S3: IAM role per Flink job (least privilege)
• EKS: IRSA — pod-level IAM role (no node credentials)
• MSK in VPC private subnets, no public endpoint
• No credentials in code — K8s Secrets / Param Store" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#bfdbfe;strokeColor=#3b82f6;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1078" y="1000" width="574" height="118" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="80" value="VPC layout: MSK brokers on 10.30.x.x
Flink TaskManagers in same VPC / SG
All traffic stays within AWS network" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=8;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1078" y="1130" width="574" height="24" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="81" value="Monitoring &amp; Alerting" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fdf4ff;strokeColor=#9333ea;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1060" y="1172" width="610" height="198" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="82" value="Amazon CloudWatch
• MSK consumer-group lag per topic → HPA trigger
• Flink job health via REST API (metrics scrape)
• S3 Bronze object count / size (data gap detection)
• DLQ message rate alarm: &gt; 1 % → PagerDuty
• Flink job FAILED alarm → SNS → on-call rotation" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e9d5ff;strokeColor=#9333ea;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1078" y="1206" width="574" height="118" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="83" value="Optional: Flink metrics → Prometheus + Grafana
Iceberg table metrics via Glue / Athena metadata" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=8;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1078" y="1336" width="574" height="24" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="84" value="Performance" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff7ed;strokeColor=#c2410c;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1060" y="1378" width="610" height="130" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="85" value="• Parquet + Snappy: ~10:1 vs JSON; predicate pushdown
• Hive-style date partitions → Athena cost reduction
• Flink pipelined execution: no shuffle between operators
• RocksDB incremental checkpoints: delta only (~3 MB @ 50 K/s)
• Iceberg metadata caching: fast split planning
• MSK: large batch fetching reduces round-trips" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=8;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1078" y="1410" width="574" height="88" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
